<p>
  <span class="nym">Maria</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">Masc. of <a class="nym" href="Mary">Mary</a>.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>Forms of <i>Mary</i> were used by men in France and Italy in the 16th C, often as a second given name or as part of a compound name.</p>
</div>
  


<dl>
<dt><span class="area">France</span></dt>
<dd>
<dl>
<dt><span class="lang">Middle French</span></dt>
